<div id="wiki-tab-0-1" style="display:none">
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc0"><span>No.003</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc1"><span><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-file-no003" target="_blank">鯛堡</a></span></h1>
<p>&quot;鯛堡&quot;是無迴轉者的壽司陀螺，某種意義上也可說是野生壽司的鯛魚握飯。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc2"><span>No.007</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc3"><span><a href="javascript:;">LSD壽司</a></span></h1>
<p>其為將致幻劑固化的食材。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc4"><span>No.021</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc5"><span><a href="javascript:;">酪梨蝦</a></span></h1>
<p>知曉酪梨與壽司的相合性，為歐美風壽司的代表。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc6"><span>No.033</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc7"><span><a href="javascript:;">量產型鯛堡</a></span></h1>
<p>由於養殖技術的發達，重現鯛堡的研究成功了。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc8"><span>No.033<span style="color: red">-D</span></span></h2>
<h1 id="toc9"><span><span style="text-decoration: line-through;"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-file-no033-d" target="_blank">貨車</a></span></span></h1>
<p><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">貨車是具有主要用來搬運貨物的裝貨台之車輛。</span></p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc10"><span>No.038</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc11"><span><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-case-file-nihira" target="_blank">假幣握飯</a></span></h1>
<p>&quot;假幣握飯&quot;是指稱由闇壽司協助，以特定的怪異憑依於食材的壽司。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc12"><span>No.039</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc13"><span><a href="javascript:;">壓力的佃煮軍艦</a></span></h1>
<p>將壓力作為軍艦壽司的食材捏握，為概念握飯之一。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc14"><span>No.041</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc15"><span><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-file-no041" target="_blank">手裏劍</a></span></h1>
<p>手裏劍為箱壽司壓縮加工後的一種型態。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc16"><span>No.042</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc17"><span><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-file-no042" target="_blank">加州卷</a></span></h1>
<p>加州卷這個名稱並非是給特定食材，其是基於形狀或料理方式所分類的。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc18"><span>No.052</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc19"><span><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-file-no052" target="_blank">磁道砲</a></span></h1>
<p>磁道砲是將物體以洛倫茲力加速，並發射出去的裝置。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc20"><span>No.053</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc21"><span><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-file-053" target="_blank">紅豆軍艦</a></span></h1>
<p>紅豆軍艦是起源於香港的一種當地壽司，主要以醋飯、海苔以及混合蛋黃醬蒸煮的紅豆沙所構成。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc22"><span>No.058</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc23"><span><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-file-no058" target="_blank">劣食壽司</a></span></h1>
<p>&quot;劣食壽司&quot;一般是指不熟練的壽司職人所作，作得很差的壽司。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc24"><span>No.064</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc25"><span><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-file-no064" target="_blank">失傳壽司</a></span></h1>
<p>&quot;失傳壽司&quot;是因為什麼理由而丟失了捏握技術，於不久後其存在也被忘記的壽司總稱。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc26"><span>No.073</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc27"><span><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-file-no073" target="_blank">原初之壽司</a></span></h1>
<p>首個被捏握、厌恶、浸渍的&quot;壽司&quot;之形，其實力是如何呢。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc28"><span>No.086</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc29"><span><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-file-no086" target="_blank">生火腿壽司</a></span></h1>
<p>生火腿壽司是從生火腿塊切取少量的生火腿，並盛放在醋飯之上的壽司。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc30"><span>No.089<span style="color: red">-D</span></span></h2>
<h1 id="toc31"><span><span style="text-decoration: line-through;"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-file-no033-d" target="_blank">炸彈握飯</a></span></span></h1>
<p><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">能用大砲直接向對手投擲的壽司陀螺。</span></p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc32"><span>No.096</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc33"><span><a href="javascript:;">金槍鰹魚壽司主義</a></span></h1>
<p>左手是究極金槍，右手是炙燒焦糖鰹。以漁夫的態疊加中誕生！這就是我的金槍鰹魚&quot;壽司&quot;主義噠ッッッ！！</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc34"><span>No.098</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc35"><span><a href="javascript:;">凱撒沙拉</a></span></h1>
<p>凱撒沙拉可說是那位凱撒所愛過的壽司。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc36"><span>No.107</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc37"><span><a href="javascript:;">瀧太郎</a></span></h1>
<p>全長3m的巨大魚類，以UMA壽司而言是入門款。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc38"><span>No.110</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc39"><span><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-file-no110" target="_blank">槍械</a></span></h1>
<p>槍械，指的是以火藥等將稱為子彈的飛行體發射出去的裝置總稱。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc40"><span>No.118</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc41"><span><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-file-no118" target="_blank">二重身</a></span></h1>
<p>二重身是自古以來流傳的超常現象之一。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc42"><span>No.157</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc43"><span><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-file-no157" target="_blank">麻辣拉麵</a></span></h1>
<p>麻辣拉麵是使用了辣椒及山椒、特徵為麻辣味的拉麵。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc44"><span>No.221</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc45"><span><a href="javascript:;">帕秋莉·諾蕾基（眼鏡）</a></span></h1>
<p>其運用厄爾瑪聖印奇術所作出。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc46"><span>No.233</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc47"><span><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-file-no233" target="_blank">简体字卷</a></span></h1>
<p>使用中国大陆所用的简体汉字，为概念握饭的一种形态。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc48"><span>No.280</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc49"><span><a href="javascript:;">特拉亞博士</a></span></h1>
<p>「就是我自身成為壽司這件事」</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc50"><span>No.303</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc51"><span><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-file-no303" target="_blank">奇哥</a></span></h1>
<p>&quot;奇哥&quot;是一種壽司形態，為一個壽司包著從外表無法預測的要素。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc52"><span>No.333</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc53"><span><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-file-no333" target="_blank">狀態握飯</a></span></h1>
<p>&quot;狀態握飯&quot;為將人類或物體的&quot;狀態&quot;作為食材的壽司總稱。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc54"><span>No.401</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc55"><span><a href="javascript:;">酸辣湯麵</a></span></h1>
<p>將表現酸味的&quot;酸&quot;加上&quot;辣&quot;，兩者兼備的拉麵。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc56"><span>No.403</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc57"><span><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-file-no403" target="_blank">握把柄</a></span></h1>
<p>&quot;握把柄&quot;為將人類&quot;弱小&quot;的記憶作為食材使用的握壽司總稱。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc58"><span>No.422</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc59"><span><a href="javascript:;">大王烏賊握飯</a></span></h1>
<p>以馬里亞納海溝的探索所供應的大王烏賊作握壽司。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc60"><span>No.499</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc61"><span><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-file-no499" target="_blank">墨魚汁意麵</a></span></h1>
<p>墨魚汁意麵是將烏賊汁作為醬汁使用、威尼斯代表的意麵料理。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc62"><span>No.514</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc63"><span><a href="javascript:;">和平握飯</a></span></h1>
<p>&quot;夜鷹機關&quot;餘黨所使用的概念壽司，能展開將各種武器無效化的壽司氣場。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc64"><span>No.555</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc65"><span><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/can-you-feel-yamizushi-file-555" target="_blank">音軌#55： Can You Feel？ / 你可感受到？</a></span></h1>
<p><em>Can You Feel？來說說小星星吧</em></p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc66"><span>No.795<span style="color: red">-D</span></span></h2>
<h1 id="toc67"><span><span style="text-decoration: line-through;"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-file-no795-d">地球</a></span></span></h1>
<p><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">地球是孕育包括人類的多個生命的，太陽系的行星。</span></p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc68"><span>No.872</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc69"><span><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-file-no872" target="_blank">歐戈波戈</a></span></h1>
<p>歐戈波戈(Ogopogo)是在加拿大不列顛哥倫比亞省的奧卡納干湖目擊到的未確認生物(UMA)。</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000000">
<h2 id="toc70"><span>No.876</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc71"><span><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yamizushi-file-no876" target="_blank">Salmon Ride</a></span></h1>
<p>雖然本體為碟形終端，但回轉時會從終端出現具有質量的幻影。</p>
</div>
